scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 2-210 comprise the full Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, starting with the heading 'SCHEDULE' and including all the negotiated terms between the parties. The content is divided into Parts 1-7, which is standard for an ISDA Schedule. The lines before line 2 are cover/exhibit references, and lines after 210 are signatures and page breaks. No CSA annexes or standard pre-print Master Agreement text is included in this span.
